data.description: Amazing opportunity for family of any size, one to many! Many amenities including granite counters, center island for prep work or serving with a raised bar, four bedrooms, great closet and storage space,  security system, sprinkler system, fenced yard, covered patio facing east-great for coffee  and sunshine in the morning and cool shade in the evening. Neighborhood pool and tot lot is just down the street and walking paths with access to the city trails and Lion's Junction park and pool. Close to Baylor, Scott & White and VA Hospitals, access to freeways to Waco or Austin.
